title: Hazing? Police look into incident at high school
text:
Police investigate alleged hazing at high school UPDATED 9:33 AM EDT Oct 22, 2015 
Police in southern York County are investigating an alleged hazing incident at Susquehannock High School. Related 
The southern York County School District superintendent confirms police were called after reports of a locker room hazing incident last Friday. 
The alleged incident involved the ninth-grade football team. 
The superintendent declined to reveal any specifics of the incident.
